WordPress co-founding developer Matt Mullenweg says his company hasn’t given up on bitcoin, despite its disappearance from his platform’s checkout page.

Speaking to CoinDesk, Mullenweg said the decision to axe bitcoin came as a result of resource constraints during WordPress’ push to streamline its five-year-old payments system – not a change of heart.
